{"tid":2177323,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台海危機期間，去台灣嘅航線應該短期內都無法使用","createTime":"2020-08-27T15:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T17:24:31.000Z","uid":109462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2062d443c945f462991e569c5fa9eb25a195b7b","tid":2177323,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"今次出走事敗，有人懷疑係咪走漏風聲、抑或中共刻意收網，但其實更大可能係佢哋一頭撞上咗中共南海軍演嘅外圍警戒部隊。最近台海情勢緊張，中共舉辦軍演威嚇東沙島，隨時準備打仗，可以預期共軍會嚴格監控東南沿海，雖然主因唔係因為要堵截逃亡者，但戒備肯定比以前更加森嚴。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>@央視軍事 8月23日消息，據廣東海事局消息，<strong><span class=\"red\">8月24日0時至8月29日24時，南海粵東海域將進行軍事訓練。</span></strong>據大連海事局消息，8月24日8時至8月25日18時，渤海海峽執行軍事任務。據唐山海事局消息，8月24日0時至9月30日24時，渤海部分海域執行實彈射擊活動。據青島海事局消息，8月22日12時至8月26日12時，黃海青島至連雲港以東海域組織重大軍事活動。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200823/36116946.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200823%2F36116946.html&d=Bx5vHrS2V4FMjGMjdccONlYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c6ce79d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20200823/36116946.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"41e78e1d0bbe86216de6bc219d7b52f4197e144f","tid":2177323,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5032c03aa599c6687299a0c2fb5c86d93eec61a7","tid":2177323,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"大家要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac3117d628fb1a75f236367cbb2f32041200ddb","tid":2177323,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig